  Agent Orchestration
  Choose how Codex should split exploration and implementation.

› 1. Auto (current)  Default. Prefer explorer agents for separable multi-file
                     discovery.
  2. Work            Use explorer agents for discovery and worker agents for
                     disjoint implementation.
  3. Agentic coding  Full orchestration plus preferred exploration subagents.
  4. Full            Use explorer and worker agents for separable coding work.
  5. Disable         Do not add orchestration guidance.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
